emablefemalecousin78]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Happy 74th Birthday Elvira, Mistress of the Dark! (Cassandra Peterson)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LfLqIij</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/W2oyUVw.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Born: Cassandra Gay Peterson
September 17, 1951, Manhattan, Kansas, U.S.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5dVTMUK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dzVjBht.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA - OCTOBER 19: Actress Cassandra Peterson attends The Groundlings' 50th Anniversary Party at Jonathan Club on October 19, 2024 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Amanda Edwards/Getty Images)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LfLqIij</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tolson9]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I devote this dump to YOUR wife so I can close tabs, pt 42 ft. the majestic skedaddle bird and all the Arepo I'm aware of.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0cLUf4G</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RDxJP2z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It is actually Wednesday, my dudes, dudettes, and others. Gentle reminder to take your meds and hydrate. Take your meds with a full glass of water! That's how they're made to be taken!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zSfDmfz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Your swamp will dry out if you don't drink water. Be the bog you want to see in the world. Maintain your biodiversity!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KvjjtDy.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love this. Some comic book writers better be taking notes on this fantastic idea.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MHIXdEP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Where are you going, birb? Do you have somewhere to be? Some pressing appointment, perhaps?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BusBum8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I fucking love these. Happy happy birthday, happy birthday youuu</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1JEVDdX.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The last time I saw something by this guy was with the whole CIA Contra cocaine thing. Good stuff.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AEgOuo6.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Gently spike the raccoon. Wham-splat, coon's a jumper for sure.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9fite46.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So goddamn good. Oh, dang. I bet a loop of this would make to fall asleep to, especially if another song is keeping you up.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lJdCRwv.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>How do you even come up with this concept...?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/edxL20w.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Aw. Chimp friend. As I commented on someone else's post, this shows that at least one chimp recognizes that our smiles are not dominance displays, but signs of friendship. Crazy that they're learning that their instincts aren't the be-all, end-all of social interaction.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/r2diNSd.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Mm... monke.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/N4qdzTP.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'm feeling good about my odds here.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ys41Ksi.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I find stuff like this absolutely fascinating. Same with the one where they show how they set concrete in rivers for bridges. If there's a youtube channel for this kind of visual learning, I'd love to know about it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cqT8pCH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bread is so good, though. Love me some french bread. Barely toasted, plenty of butter.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5wK5RLF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Shine on, you funky little dinosaur. Peepeepeep!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TuNxkQc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's wednesday, but we can still get tacos. Who's with me?!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x5xFYnh.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yep, fair. You and me both, sleep paralysis demon. You and me both.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XnzyvsT.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What a trip. Idk, I think I'd do... most of that stuff. Probably not heroin, though.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qnoP1bc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Squid! Noodle!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ix6f4UC.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I wonder if she got it eventually.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CzW2JfK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hangry gato has much to say.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5rTHlVD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>patapatapatapata</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0cLUf4G</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[J4nein4ne]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cat brings her kittens every night to her human’s bed</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2BDn1h7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QI5gPUf.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2BDn1h7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sholiPiPrince]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hearing his bark for a first time</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xP7fpDL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nJdJ5vT.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xP7fpDL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MedicalScience]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>